375
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,550
Kami di sini.

376
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:56,880
Baiklah.

377
00:27:57,470 --> 00:28:00,010
Adakah anda tahu mengapa saya memilih Shi Yuxiang?

378
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,880
